<ul>
<li><span class="plainlinksneverexpand"><code><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.freebsd.org/cgi/man.cgi?query=chroot&amp;sektion=2">chroot(2)</a></code></span>:&#160;change root directory&#160;–&#160;<a href="FreeBSD.html" title="FreeBSD">FreeBSD</a> System Calls <a href="Manual_page_(Unix).html" title="Manual page (Unix)" class="mw-redirect">Manual</a></li>
<li><span class="plainlinksneverexpand"><code><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.freebsd.org/cgi/man.cgi?query=chroot&amp;sektion=8">chroot(8)</a></code></span>:&#160;change root directory&#160;–&#160;<a href="FreeBSD.html" title="FreeBSD">FreeBSD</a> System Manager's <a href="Manual_page_(Unix).html" title="Manual page (Unix)" class="mw-redirect">Manual</a></li>
<li><span class="plainlinksneverexpand"><code><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.kernel.org/doc/man-pages/online/pages/man2/chroot.2.html">chroot(2)</a></code></span>:&#160;change root directory&#160;–&#160;<a href="Linux.html" title="Linux">Linux</a> Programmer's <a href="Manual_page_(Unix).html" title="Manual page (Unix)" class="mw-redirect">Manual</a> – System Calls</li>
